byline.contributor: Anne Barnard contributed reporting from Beirut, Lebanon.

abstract: Russian officials say technical failure resulted in MIG-29 fighter jet crashing off Syrian coast.
lead_paragraph: The Russian Defense Ministry blamed a technical failure for the crash of the jet, a MIG-29.
